Installation instructions for GeneMarkS-2 software

Download the key file from http://topaz.gatech.edu/GeneMark/license_download.cgi
Install key file into user's home directory as

  cp some-key-file   ~/.gmhmmp2_key

Note: substitute the name "some-key-file" by the name of file from download.

Attention, key file is renamed into hidden system file by above command.

Copy the content of distribution to desired location.
Program is ready for execution.

Perl scripts are configured with default Perl location at "/usr/bin/perl"

#================================================

